# SparkMatch mobile — environment configuration
#
# Copy to ".env" and adjust. All Expo public vars must start with EXPO_PUBLIC_.
#
# In development the app auto-detects your machine's LAN IP from the Expo dev
# server, so you usually do NOT need to set this. Override only if auto-detection
# fails (e.g. VPN, custom network) or to point at a remote/staging backend.
#
# Examples:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.42:8080
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.sparkmatch.com
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
